findings.title: Owner can mint any amounts of tokens before transferring ownership to MasterChef
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to mint any amount of tokens before transferring ownership to MasterChef.

findings.title: Owner can change fee rate
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the fee rate.

findings.title: Owner can change fee address wallet
findings.description: The contract owner has the privilege to modify the fee address wallet.

findings.title: Owner can add / remove fee whitelist addresses
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to add or remove fee whitelist addresses before transferring ownership to MasterChef.

findings.title: Owner can add / remove dex pairs
findings.description: The contract owner has the privilege to add or remove dex pairs without any restrictions.

findings.title: Owner can add / remove minters
findings.description: The owner has privileges to add or remove minters, which could lead to unauthorized token minting.

findings.title: Minters can mint tokens up to max supply amount to any address
findings.description: Minters have the privilege to mint tokens up to the maximum supply amount and transfer them to any desired address.
